name: RETRO LIVERY! Cargolux Boeing 747-400 Freighter in Action at Calgary Airport
description:
Cargolux is Calgary's only Boeing 747 operator, serving the city twice weekly with a mix of Boeing 747-400 and 747-8 Freighters.

This particular 747 joined the Cargolux fleet last year, and was painted in this striking 50th anniversary retro livery.

Cargolux in Calgary during the daytime is already a fairly rare occurrence, but seeing their retro 747 is just icing on the cake! Enjoy this retro 747 action.
